    "data": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You launch three projectiles at points you can see within range. Each creature within a 10-foot radius sphere of each point must make a Dexterity saving throw. A creature takes 3d6 fire and 3d6 kinetic damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature in the area of more than one sphere is affected only once.</p>\n<p>The power damages objects in the area and ignites flammable objects that aren't being worn or carried.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Overcharge Tech.</strong></em> When you cast this power using a tech slot of 6th level or higher, you create four projectiles. When you cast this power using a tech slot of 8th level or higher, you create five projectiles.</p>\n",
